    hakaisalmon

    Brett Johnson

    2018-04-04

    hakaisalmon.Rmd

    The purpose of this package is to make as easy as possible the loading of salmon program data, and store custom functions for summarizing program data quickly and in one place.

    To be edited below if necessary: ## Figures

    The figure sizes have been customised so that you can easily put two images side-by-side.

    plot(1:10)
plot(10:1)

    You can enable figure captions by fig_caption: yes in YAML:

    output:
  rmarkdown::html_vignette:
    fig_caption: yes

    Then you can use the chunk option fig.cap = "Your figure caption." in knitr.
